<!-- What is src?
Ans: src = source. Specifies the location of a digital source. -->
<!-- Why are some tags self-closing but others are not?
Ans: Self-closing tags represent void elements. Void elements like img and br cannot contain any content. All other tags may (but are not required to) contain content. -->


